My first chart

set.seed(42)
ggplot (diamonds %>% sample_n(500),
        aes (carat, price))+
  geom_point()+
  geom_smooth()
## `geom_smooth()` using method = 'loess' and formula = 'y ~ x'

We found a positive relationship between two variables.

Another chart

ggplot (diamonds, mapping = aes(cut, fill=color)) +
  geom_bar(position = "fill") +
  theme_minimal()
